{"tid":1878924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（豆腐沙中線）大家係咪放過咗黨鐵，唔該同我煲返大紅磡同土瓜灣！！！","createTime":"2020-02-14T01:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T02:43:39.000Z","uid":258731,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1109d94160e44616396f2a791cc18d66c28db457","tid":1878924,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:18:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xcpc60m8rTY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fxcpc60m8rTY&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5Ivc3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=f0401ecb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xcpc60m8rTY</a><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;豆腐沙中線&rdquo;紅磡站開鑿發現6成鋼筋不達標<br />\n香港地鐵沙中線，恐怕淪為豆腐渣工程。港鐵上周開始在沙中線紅磡站開鑿水泥檢查施工情況，運輸及房屋局21日再公布7支鋼筋的檢測結果，當中3支與螺絲帽接駁不達標，其中一支鋼筋的螺絲頭僅扭入螺絲帽約6毫米，遠低於至少扭入40毫米的要求，港鐵更發現有未經接駁的螺絲帽。連同周三公布的3支，港鐵暫檢測到的10支鋼筋中有6支不達標。換言之，在開鑿檢驗的鋼筋中，有6成不達標。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/amp.rfi.fr/tw/%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%258F%25B0/20181223-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%25B1%2586%25E8%2585%2590%25E6%25B2%2599%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25B7%259A%25E7%25B4%2585%25E7%25A3%25A1%25E7%25AB%2599%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%2591%25BF%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE6%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%258B%25BC%25E7%25AD%258B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%25A8%2599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Famp.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%2525E6%2525B8%2525AF%2525E6%2525BE%2525B3%2525E5%25258F%2525B0%2F20181223-%2525E5%25259C%2525B0%2525E9%252590%2525B5%2525E8%2525B1%252586%2525E8%252585%252590%2525E6%2525B2%252599%2525E4%2525B8%2525AD%2525E7%2525B7%25259A%2525E7%2525B4%252585%2525E7%2525A3%2525A1%2525E7%2525AB%252599%2525E9%252596%25258B%2525E9%252591%2525BF%2525E7%252599%2525BC%2525E7%25258F%2525BE6%2525E6%252588%252590%2525E9%25258B%2525BC%2525E7%2525AD%25258B%2525E4%2525B8%25258D%2525E9%252581%252594%2525E6%2525A8%252599&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5Ivc3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=27d2ffd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www